<L>__{47i the truck can't fit on either side. neither can it stop, at that}
<A>__{speed. tires locked, it slides on the muddy concrete and piles into the concrete abutment at seventy.}
<L>__{47j terminator and john emerge from the tunnel, looking back to see a}
<A>__{fireball blasting through behind them as the truck's side tanks explode. terminator stops the harley. john peers around his body to see the destruction. a burning wheel wobbles out of the tunnel and flops in the mud. terminator revs the bike and they roar away, down the canal, disappearing around a bend.}
